{"tid":1506184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[道歉] 啱啱喺火車嗰位巴打 好對唔住","createTime":"2019-08-25T17:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T17:40:34.000Z","uid":141577,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1e8c9f65187bcc34461db0fa7ac26595fb37d9b1","tid":1506184,"uid":141577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:33:07.000Z","msg":"喺車上面鬧你嚇親你sorry<br />\n見你喺紅磡上車<br />\n架車一開你就除低眼罩口罩<br />\n但全架車好多都唔係自己友黎<br />\n又難確保無cctvb 上車影人樣<br />\n好唔想大家因為一絲鬆懈就俾人拉 俾人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位手足都係 警戒心要強啲<br />\n最唔應該除罩嘅地方就係喺地鐵火車<br />\n仲有我仲見到好多豬咀兄弟竟然係無blackbloc<br />\n你唔驚俾人拉 我驚你俾人拉呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求求大家 小心啲啦好嘛<br />\n我真係好愛大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9aeb8c92cb0fbb67c174240334c36193ca5e4f4","tid":1506184,"uid":164705,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:35:45.000Z","msg":"記得要語氣好d，長期運動大家都要練eq"},{"pid":"b6e6d2b34044c82edd541b012e61e0204df7e605","tid":1506184,"uid":206812,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:37:00.000Z","msg":"家母一路睇電視 見好多人爬山嘅時候<br />\n俾狗咬住個背囊走唔甩 咬到好傷好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以用師奶思想 建議大家<br />\n行山嘅時候 個書包入面裝水裝紙巾好喇<br />\n至於你啲身分證 或者電話其他重要嘢<br />\n有腰包就放腰包（要戴係面衫<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">裡面</span></span>啊懵佬）<br />\n無就好似呀婆咁 著條有袋/拉鍊嘅背心底衫喇<br />\n你知啲動物好鍾意咬住個袋唔放 唔俾你走<br />\n只要你個袋無重要嘢 就可以嚟一招<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">金蟬脫殼</span></span><br />\n<br />\n示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0JGmV6t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0JGmV6t.png&h=1aa75a82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小心個袋俾狗咬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506145\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506145</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d9dc918624fc6db68627e4b2249fc8059f8bb9cd","tid":1506184,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:37:50.000Z","msg":"明白了，下次唔會"},{"pid":"a12df4a5f872895254e48764fb3bc827e69f2460","tid":1506184,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:39:22.000Z","msg":"一腔熱血 忘記自身安危"},{"pid":"735e2a938533e813bbfe6e85a3eefaf9e038db0d","tid":1506184,"uid":141577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9aeb8c92cb0fbb67c174240334c36193ca5e4f4","tid":1506184,"uid":164705,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:35:45.000Z","msg":"記得要語氣好d，長期運動大家都要練eq"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:39:36.000Z","msg":"下次會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7381ed8828829b1767defc3852d2e0a3a544f2cf","tid":1506184,"uid":31710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:40:34.000Z","msg":"［緊急！］反對曾偉雄既白宮聯署有問題！多人表示收唔到確認email!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1503718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1503718</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n個petition已經24個小時冇郁過個人數！！！<br />\n懷疑中共做左手腳"}]}